- Foreign words (French?) are carved on the inner faces of both the boards: “Bain” and “Ruel” (front, back boards respectively).&#xD;
- Writing exercises, doodles; in pen and pencil, on fols. 1rv, 2r, 23v, 37v, 41v, 61, 62.</item>
